---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Shipping, Returns & Delivery - KitchingArt"
  description="KitchingArt shipping information. No import taxes or tariffs in the US, Canada, UK, EU, GCC countries, Singapore or Australia."
>
  <section class="shipping-page section">
    <div class="container shipping-content">
      <h1>Shipping, returns etc</h1>

      <div class="shipping-body">
        <h2>Shipping destinations</h2>
        <p>Your picture will be produced on demand according to your specification in either the US, Canada, the UK, the EU, Dubai, Singapore or Australia, depending on where you're located.</p>

        <p><strong>No import taxes or tariffs</strong> in the US, Canada, the UK, the EU, GCC countries, Singapore or Australia.</p>

        <h2>Delivery times</h2>
        <p>Securely delivered in five to seven days, ready to hang.</p>

        <h2>Production</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Fine quality giclee printed canvas of 340gsm in weight.</li>
          <li>Vibrant colours from water-based HP Latex inks and UV protection.</li>
          <li>Choose from black or white wood based frames, or go frameless if you prefer.</li>
          <li>Multiple sizes available.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Returns</h2>
        <p>If you're not happy with your purchase, please contact me directly and we'll sort it out. I want you to be satisfied with your art.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .shipping-content {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .shipping-content h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .shipping-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .shipping-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .shipping-body ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .shipping-body li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
